The paper discusses the security requirements of online lotteries and proposes a novel distributed protocol that applies techniques developed for voting applications. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed systems (cs.DS), game theory (cs.GT), and possibly data structures and algorithms (cs.DC) as the proposed protocol involves efficient verification of the random process.
